	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=107160><span id= >mrjimorg</span></a><br><span id=notbold>78 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.36]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>The first time I just talked with Sentry Xyrinn (what boat accident?, what potion of marr?). She went up to stand next to the specs, never fought them and dropped this item before despawning. This could be done at level 1. The item was 18/40.<br>The third time I did this, I asked &quot;what boat accident&quot;, then gave her the potion of marr. She despawned immediately and said something like &quot;Thank you for the potion. I have been summoned elsewhere&quot;. She didn't leave anything behind and didn't fight the specs.<br>The second time I gave her the potion right away, but forgot to cast my faction modifier first so she said I hadn't helped the temple or marr enough. She did the same as the first attempt.<br>The fourth time I asked her both questions, then gave her the potion. She despawned again, said she was summoned and dropped nothing again.<br>When I returned the empty potion of marr to the the temple of marr I got the spell stun. So, to recap - give her the potion and you dont get the weapon. Just hail her and follow the verbal queues and you'll get it. Seems kinda backwards.<br>I did not try giving her the potion before hailing here. Not sure what that will do, but I assume she would despawn.<br>As for the stats, they were 18/40. Never saw 20/40. Perhaps you guys could post a link. Are you sure your not thinking of another item?<br>To make her spawn, just go to sister isle to the little hut by the docks (not the double hut). There is a woman inside named either &quot;Paeonia Purnn&quot; or &quot;Phocaea Hapspenn&quot;- I dont remember which. Tell her &quot;Where is Sentry Xyrinn?&quot;. Good luck<br>-Ollex<br></p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
